Release Notes:

Originally formed a dozen years ago while students together at Indiana University, the a cappella group has reassembled and  reemerged after their video for &#039;The Twelve Days of Christmas&#039; became a phenomenon with almost 8 million views on YouTube. In an era when so much pop music is the product of digital processing and vocal pro-tooling, Straight No Chaser is the real deal- the captivating sound of ten unadulterated human voices coming together to make extraordinary music that is moving people in a fundamental sense...and with a sense of humor.
